# Legacy atlas URL redirects → /atlas/<slug>.
# All atlas content shares one global slug namespace, so the destination is
# just /atlas/<slug> regardless of kind. The SPA also handles these via
# in-app <Navigate> for client-side navigation; this file covers direct
# requests, search engines, and inbound external links.
/algorithms                /atlas                  301
/algorithms/models         /atlas?kind=model       301
/algorithms/models/:slug   /atlas/:slug            301
/algorithms/:slug          /atlas/:slug            301
/concepts/:slug            /atlas/:slug            301
